            <h4 class="skills-content-text-box-heading">C</h4>
            <p>C is a high-level, general-purpose, procedural programming language. It provides low-level memory
              access and can run natively with minimal runtime support. It makes C suitable for operating systems,
              databases, compilers, and embedded systems development. </p>
            <code class="skills-content-text-box-code">printf("Hey Jude\n");</code>
